    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Distribution of Omalium in the Himalayan region: O. acutangulum sp. n. (circles), O. amplissimum sp. n. (star), O. beesoni (squares), O. cariosum (diamonds), O. flavotestaceum sp. n. (triangles)." ;
